013package org.apache.juneau.cp;
014
015import java.lang.reflect.*;
016import java.util.*;
017
018/**
019 * A simple list of {@link Method} objects.
020 *
021 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
022 * </ul>
023 *
024 * @serial exclude
025 */
026public class MethodList extends ArrayList<Method> {
027   private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;
028
029   /**
030    * Creator.
031    *
032    * @param methods The methods to add to this list.
033    * @return A new list of methods.
034    */
035   public static MethodList of(Collection<Method> methods) {
036      return new MethodList(methods);
037   }
038
039   /**
040    * Constructor.
041    */
042   public MethodList() {}
043
044   /**
045    * Constructor.
046    *
047    * @param methods The methods to add to this list.
048    */
049   public MethodList(Collection<Method> methods) {
050      super(methods);
051   }
052
053}
